            "title": "<p>GLP-1s slow everything down. (Including your digestion.)</p>",
            "body": "<p>That's literally how they work — slower stomach, smaller appetite, less food. But the same mechanism that kills your hunger also backs up everything downstream. Bloat. Discomfort. Mornings that just don't move the way they used to. Coffee plus prebiotics keeps things moving. Not harsh. Not urgent. Just regular again.</p>",
