            "body": "<p>That's why mid-morning hits you shaky, foggy, and off — even when food doesn't sound appealing at all. You don't need a full breakfast. You need something your body can actually use, in a format your appetite will still say yes to. A cold iced coffee takes about ten seconds to make. That's a format that works.</p>",
