            "title": "<p>Protect your muscle while the weight comes off</p>",
            "body": "<p>A GLP-1 can quietly cost you strength, tone, and metabolism — especially once protein intake drops alongside appetite. The goal was never to just weigh less. It was to look and feel better in the process. Twenty grams of protein before lunch, every morning, without cooking or choking down a shake, is one of the simplest ways to protect that.</p>",
