            "title": "<p>Under-fueled energy hits different when you're on a GLP-1</p>",
            "body": "<p>Eating less. Somehow even more tired. Sound familiar? Caffeine alone is a short-term patch — that's why the afternoon crash keeps showing up even though \"nothing changed.\" Franky pairs 100mg of natural caffeine with 200mg of L-theanine specifically to smooth the curve. No jitter spike. No 11am dip. Just steady focus through your morning.</p>",
