            "title": "<p>If it's not easy, it won't stick</p>",
            "body": "<p>You're not cooking breakfast on a low-appetite morning. You're not choking down a thick protein shake before you're even awake. The only routine that survives a GLP-1 is the one that barely feels like a routine. Two scoops. Cold water or milk. Ice. Sixty seconds. That's it.</p>",
